: BUILD PREREQUISITES
Library requires an Nvidia GPU with compute capability of 3.0 or higher.
Compute capability of your device can be found on Nvidia's CUDA Developer
site: https://developer.nvidia.com/cuda-gpus.
Alternatively, if the CUDA Samples are installed, you may also find it by
running deviceQuery and finding the following line:
--> CUDA Capability Major/Minor version number

: AUTOTOOLS BUILD & INSTALL
autoreconf -ivf && ./configure && make
sudo make install

: THANKS
Autotools + CUDA derived from ClusterChimps
www.clusterchimps.org